Chemistry/InternalCoords version 0.17
=====================================

This modules convert from internal to Cartesian coordinates and viceversa.

CHANGES SINCE VERSION 0.16
    - Handle linear angles.
    - Minor POD corrections.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:
        "Chemistry::Mol" => "0.25",
        "Scalar::Util" => 0,
        "Chemistry::Canonicalize" => 0.10,
        "Chemistry::Bond::Find" => 0.20,

